00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:29.290
Think about preference
describing in economics.

00:00:29.290 --> 00:00:30.910
What do people want?

00:00:30.910 --> 00:00:33.015
What makes them happy
in one way or the other?

00:00:33.015 --> 00:00:35.140
We talked about time
preferences, risk preferences,

00:00:35.140 --> 00:00:37.430
