If they pay attention,
they should really

00:14:35.950 --> 00:14:38.260
know what's going on,
and they should really--

00:14:38.260 --> 00:14:40.600
the stock market should go up.

00:14:40.600 --> 00:14:44.980
Conditional on that, on the
