00:15:01.662 --> 00:15:02.620
So stocks should go up.

00:15:02.620 --> 00:15:06.250
So really, if there's
full attention,

00:15:06.250 --> 00:15:10.030
you expect nothing to
happen on May 3, '98.

00:15:10.030 --> 00:15:12.340
And then if there's a
failed replication, well,

00:15:12.340 --> 00:15:18.190
