00:17:22.339 --> 00:17:25.569
Does that make sense?

00:17:25.569 --> 00:17:27.140
OK.

00:17:27.140 --> 00:17:29.390
And there's lots of examples
of these kinds of things.

00:17:29.390 --> 00:17:32.020
But essentially,
some of this is--

00:17:32.020 --> 00:17:34.288
in attention, some of
it is also confusion.

00:17:34.288 --> 00:17:35.830
I don't know if any
